  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    HbarRangeException
    Thrown by constructors/factory methods of Hbar when a value is out of range.
    HederaNetworkException
    Wrapper for all transport-related exceptions.
    HederaPrecheckStatusException
    A HederaStatusException, thrown specifically by a transaction precheck (validation on the node it was submitted to).

    A HederaStatusException, thrown on error status by TransactionId.getReceipt(Client).
    HederaRecordStatusException
    A HederaStatusException, thrown on error status by TransactionId.getRecord(Client).
    HederaStatusException
    Base class for exceptions thrown from HAPI calls that result in a Status code that is not Status.Success.
    LocalValidationException
    Thrown from TransactionBuilder.build(Client) and HederaCall.execute(Client) if the built transaction or query fails local sanity checks.
